.SH NAME
.PP
\f[B]public\-key\-get\f[] \[en] get Global/Private Virgil Public Key
from the Virgil Keys Service.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
\ \ \ \ virgil\ public\-key\-get\ \ [\-o\ <file>]\ \-e\ <arg>\ [\-V]\ [\-\-]\ [\-\-version]\ [\-h]
\f[]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
This utility allows you to get a public key by its
\f[C]public\-key\-id\f[].
.SH OPTIONS
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
\ \ \ \ \-o\ <file>,\ \ \-\-out\ <file>
